# NOTE: data/ is INTENTIONALLY tracked in git. The GitHub Actions
# workflows commit daily updates back to the repo so `git pull` on
# your laptop is enough to get the latest prices, predictions,
# scored news, and FIPI flows. Do not add `data/` here.
